     `xcodebuild test` actually runs the unit tests.

  Auto-generated by Sprint 4H; re-run scripts/regenerate-xcode-scheme.sh
  if the target IDs in PrivateChat.xcodeproj/project.pbxproj change.

  Reference IDs (current as of 2026-06-22):
